name: Maven-repo
body:
# [nil's maven repository](https://github.com/nil2013/maven-repo)

自作ライブラリ用のmaven repositoryです

## for SBT

```scala
resolvers += "nil's Repository on Github" at "http://nil2013.github.io/maven-repo/"
```

## Contains following

### [nil2013/LIlib](http://nil2013.github.io/LIlib/)

```scala
libraryDependencies += "me.nsmr" %% "lilib" % "1.1.3"
```

* [jar Files](https://github.com/nil2013/maven-repo/tree/master/lilib)
